#: includes/class-admin.php:588
msgid "WC Hide Price & Ask Button Pro allows you to hide product prices and replace the WooCommerce \"Add to Cart\" button with a customizable \"Ask for Product\" button. When a customer clicks this button, a contact form modal opens where they can send you an inquiry about the product. This is perfect for products that require custom quotes, exclusive items, or any product where you prefer personal communication over direct purchasing."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-admin.php:591
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-admin.php:593
msgid "Hide prices for individual products or entire categories."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-admin.php:594
msgid "Replace the Add to Cart button with a customizable inquiry button."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-admin.php:595
msgid "Built-in contact form modal — no extra plugins needed."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-admin.php:596
msgid "Inherits your theme styling for seamless integration."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-admin.php:597
msgid "Full internationalization (i18n) support."
